	<h3>Get Started in 5 EASY STEPS!</h3>
	<ol>
		<li>Access the Library Reserves tool at: <a href="https://reserves.library.nd.edu">https://reserves.library.nd.edu</a>.</li>
		<li>Select a course to begin adding Reserve items.</li>
		<li>Click on the "Add Reserve" button and select "New Reserve".</li>
		<li>Select material type.</li>
		<li>Complete the form with title, citation, and date needed. Submit when you are done.</li>
	</ol>
